<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
        {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset('css/style.css') }}" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <header class="col-xs-12 turquoise">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="pull-right">
                {% if user.status == true %}
                    <a href="{{ path('announceMy') }}" class="btn">
                        Meus anuncios
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{ path('announceNew') }}" class="btn">
                        Anunciar
                    </a>
                {% else %}
                    <a href="#" class="btn">
                        Entrar
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">
                        Criar conta
                    </a>
                {% endif %}
                </div>
                <h1>
                    <a href="{{ path('announceHome') }}">Anúncios</a>
                </h1>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="col-xs-12 green-sea bar-search">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <form class="search" action="" method="post">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Está procurando alguma coisa?" name="search"/>
                    <button type="submit"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></i></button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
        {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
        <div align="center" class="modal" id="login">
            <form method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="password" name="pwd"  class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Entrar"/>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div align="center" class="modal" id="create">
        {% if code is null %}
            <p>Olá, ainda somos beta. Você precisa de um código nosso para poder criar uma conta.</p>
            <p>Quer participar? Coloque o seu e-mail abaixo e te mandaremos um código assim que possivel.</p>
            <form method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="E-mail" class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Quero meu código"/>
            </form>
        {% else %}
            <p>Olá, obrigado por querer participar do nosso beta.</p>
            <form method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="E-mail" class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Nome" class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="password" name="pwd" placeholder="Senha" class="form-control"/>
                </div>
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Começar"/>
            </form>
        {% endif %}
        </div>
    </body>
</html>